<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Learna Account Activation</title>
    <style>
        body{
            font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height:1.6;
            background-color:#f4f4f4;
            margin:0;
            padding:0;
        }
        .container{
            max-width:600px;
            margin:auto;
            padding:20px;
            background-color:#fff;
            border-radius:5px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Account Activation</h2>
        <p>Hello <%= user.name %>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for registering an account with us. To activate your account, please click the button below:</p>
        <a href="<%= activationCode %>" class="btn">Activate Account</a>
        <p><%= activationCode %></p>
        <p>If you didn't register an account with us, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>Learna</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
